      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.25rem);font-weight:400;color:#191817;line-height:1.12;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        Selling in Chermside 2026
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(25,24,23,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Chermside is Brisbane's major northern hub: Westfield, Prince Charles Hospital, and a diverse housing market that rewards sellers who understand which buyer profile they are targeting. Here is what sellers need to know before listing in 2026.
      </p>
